><a href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/congratulations/\" class=\"thumbnail-link\"><img width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"http://badgeos.org/wp-content/uploads/edd/2014/08/congrats-badgeos-icon.png\" class=\"attachment-200x200 wp-post-image\" alt=\"Congrats Add-on for BadgeOS\" /></a><p>Automatically displays an overlay &#8220;pop-up&#8221; window congratulating users as they earn achievements.</p>\n<a class=\"button-secondary\" href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/congratulations/\">Add-On Details</a></div><div class=\"addon\"><h2>Referring Links</h2><a href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/referring-link/\" class=\"thumbnail-link\"><img width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"http://badgeos.org/wp-content/uploads/edd/2014/06/referring-link-badge.png\" class=\"attachment-200x200 wp-post-image\" alt=\"Referring Link Add-on\" /></a><p>Allows users to earn achievements or badges on your site by clicking on a link that you can place virtually anywhere.</p>\n<a class=\"button-secondary\" href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/referring-link/\">Add-On Details</a></div><div class=\"addon\"><h2>Leaderboards</h2><a href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/leaderboards/\" class=\"thumbnail-link\"><img width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"http://badgeos.org/wp-content/uploads/edd/2013/11/leaderboard-300x300.png\" class=\"attachment-200x200 wp-post-image\" alt=\"BadgeOS Leaderboards\" /></a><p>Easily create, configure and add leaderboards to your BadgeOS site. </p>\n<a class=\"button-secondary\" href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/leaderboards/\">Add-On Details</a></div><div class=\"addon\"><h2>Community</h2><a href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/community/\" class=\"thumbnail-link\"><img width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"http://badgeos.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/add-on-community-200x200.png\" class=\"attachment-200x200 wp-post-image\" alt=\"add-on-community\" /></a><p>Issue badges for a range of community activity and display them on user profiles and activity feeds, through integration with BuddyPress and bbPress.</p>\n<a class=\"button-secondary\" href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/community/\">Add-On Details</a></div><div class=\"addon\"><h2>Activity Codes</h2><a href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/activity-codes/\" class=\"thumbnail-link\"><img width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"http://badgeos.org/wp-content/uploads/edd/2013/09/activity-codes.png\" class=\"attachment-200x200 wp-post-image\" alt=\"BadgeOS Activity Codes\" /></a><p>Allow users to earn any Achievement by entering an &#8220;Activity Code&#8221; on any BadgeOS-enabled WordPress site.</p>\n<a class=\"button-secondary\" href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/activity-codes/\">Add-On Details</a></div><div class=\"addon\"><h2>Credly Login for WordPress</h2><a href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/credly-login-to-wordpress/\" class=\"thumbnail-link\"><img width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"http://badgeos.org/wp-content/uploads/edd/2013/09/credly-login2.png\" class=\"attachment-200x200 wp-post-image\" alt=\"WordPress Credly Login\" /></a><p>Log in to any WordPress site using your Credly account, without creating a new WordPress username.</p>\n<a class=\"button-secondary\" href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/credly-login-to-wordpress/\">Add-On Details</a></div><div class=\"addon\"><h2>Reports</h2><a href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/reports/\" class=\"thumbnail-link\"><img width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"http://badgeos.org/wp-content/uploads/edd/2013/09/reports.png\" class=\"attachment-200x200 wp-post-image\" alt=\"BadgeOS Reports\" /></a><p>Review achievement analytics and downloadable reports on your BadgeOS sites.</p>\n<a class=\"button-secondary\" href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/reports/\">Add-On Details</a></div><div class=\"addon\"><h2>Sensei Add-on</h2><a href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/sensei/\" class=\"thumbnail-link\"><img width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"http://badgeos.org/wp-content/uploads/edd/2013/09/woo-sensei-badge.png\" class=\"attachment-200x200 wp-post-image\" alt=\"WooThemes&#039; Sensei Add-on for BadgeOS\" /></a><p>Automatically issue BadgeOS achievements and badges for virtually every activity in the Sensei learning management system by WooThemes.</p>\n<a class=\"button-secondary\" href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/sensei/\">Add-On Details</a></div><div class=\"addon\"><h2>LearnDash</h2><a href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/learndash-add-on/\" class=\"thumbnail-link\"><img width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"http://badgeos.org/wp-content/uploads/edd/2013/09/learndash-badge.png\" class=\"attachment-200x200 wp-post-image\" alt=\"LearnDash Add-on for BadgeOS\" /></a><p>Instantly issue badges for lesson, course and quiz activity in the LearnDash learning management system.</p>\n<a class=\"button-secondary\" href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/learndash-add-on/\">Add-On Details</a></div><div class=\"addon\"><h2>Invite Codes</h2><a href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/invite-codes/\" class=\"thumbnail-link\"><img width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"http://badgeos.org/wp-content/uploads/edd/2013/09/invite-codes.png\" class=\"attachment-200x200 wp-post-image\" alt=\"BadgeOS Invite Codes\" /></a><p>Automatically join users to one or more specified BuddyPress Groups when they use a special Invite Code to join your site.</p>\n<a class=\"button-secondary\" href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/invite-codes/\">Add-On Details</a></div><div class=\"addon\"><h2>Guest Achievements</h2><a href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/guest-achievements/\" class=\"thumbnail-link\"><img width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"http://badgeos.org/wp-content/uploads/edd/2014/06/guest-earners-badges.png\" class=\"attachment-200x200 wp-post-image\" alt=\"Guest Achievements\" /></a><p>A companion add-on to allow non-logged in users to earn achievements even before they join or login.</p>\n<a class=\"button-secondary\" href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/guest-achievements/\">Add-On Details</a></div><div class=\"addon\"><h2>Auto Messages</h2><a href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/auto-messages/\" class=\"thumbnail-link\"><img width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"http://badgeos.org/wp-content/uploads/edd/2013/09/auto-messages.png\" class=\"attachment-200x200 wp-post-image\" alt=\"BadgeOS Auto Messages\" /></a><p>Trigger special messages for users after they cross particular achievement and site activity thresholds.</p>\n<a class=\"button-secondary\" href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/auto-messages/\">Add-On Details</a></div><div class=\"addon\"><h2>BadgeStack</h2><a href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/badgestack/\" class=\"thumbnail-link\"><img width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"http://badgeos.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/add-on-badgestack-200x200.png\" class=\"attachment-200x200 wp-post-image\" alt=\"BadgeStack\" /></a><p>Automatically create achievement types, pages and sample content to jumpstart your own badging system.</p>\n<a class=\"button-secondary\" href=\"http://badgeos.org/downloads/badgestack/\">Add-On Details</a></div>','no'),(108655,'_site_transient_timeout_browser_47501a773fe850ef5105e7eb40e53b58','1431625963','yes'),(108656,'_site_transient_browser_47501a773fe850ef5105e7eb40e53b58','a:9:{s:8:\"platform\";s:9:\"Macintosh\";s:4:\"name\";s:6:\"Safari\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"7.0.6\";s:10:\"update_url\";s:28:\"http://www.apple.com/safari/\";s:7:\"img_src\";s:49:\"http://s.wordpress.org/images/browsers/safari.png\";s:11:\"img_src_ssl\";s:48:\"https://wordpress.org/images/browsers/safari.png\";s:15:\"current_version\";s:1:\"5\";s:7:\"upgrade\";b:0;s:8:\"insecure\";b:0;}','yes'),(115894,'shibboleth_login_url','http://www.itercom.org/Shibboleth.sso/Login','yes'),(115895,'shibboleth_default_login','','yes'),(115896,'shibboleth_auto_login','','yes'),(115897,'shibboleth_logout_url','http://www.itercom.org/Shibboleth.sso/Logout','yes'),(115898,'shibboleth_headers','a:6:{s:8:\"username\";a:2:{s:4:\"name\";s:4:\"eppn\";s:7:\"managed\";b:0;}s:10:\"first_name\";a:2:{s:4:\"name\";s:9:\"givenName\";s:7:\"managed\";b:1;}s:9